{
  "page": "Raynard",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\" style=\"font-style: italic;padding-left: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">For the head of House Ruttiger, see <a href=\"/index.php/Raynard_Ruttiger\" title=\"Raynard Ruttiger\">Raynard Ruttiger</a>. For the Lord Commander of the Kingsguard, see <a href=\"/index.php/Raynard_Ruskyn\" title=\"Raynard Ruskyn\">Raynard Ruskyn</a>.</div>\n<table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Faith_of_the_Seven\" title=\"Faith of the Seven\"><img alt=\"Star of the Faith.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/9/91/Star_of_the_Faith.svg/50px-Star_of_the_Faith.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/9/91/Star_of_the_Faith.svg/75px-Star_of_the_Faith.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/9/91/Star_of_the_Faith.svg/100px-Star_of_the_Faith.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Septon</span><br />Raynard</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Faith_of_the_Seven\" title=\"Faith of the Seven\"><img alt=\"Star of the Faith.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/9/91/Star_of_the_Faith.svg/50px-Star_of_the_Faith.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/9/91/Star_of_the_Faith.svg/75px-Star_of_the_Faith.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/9/91/Star_of_the_Faith.svg/100px-Star_of_the_Faith.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Septon\" title=\"Septon\">Septon</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiances</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Faith_of_the_Seven\" title=\"Faith of the Seven\">Faith of the Seven</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Most_Devout\" title=\"Most Devout\">Most Devout</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Westeros\" title=\"Westeros\">Westeros</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i> (mentioned)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Raynard</b> is a septon of the <a href=\"/index.php/Faith_of_the_Seven\" title=\"Faith of the Seven\">Faith of the Seven</a>. He is stationed in <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc17.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc17.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> and is of the <a href=\"/index.php/Most_Devout\" title=\"Most Devout\">Most Devout</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc28.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc28.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Raynard&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Feast_for_Crows\"><i>A Feast for Crows</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Raynard&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Feast for Crows\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Raynard informs the <a href=\"/index.php/Small_council\" title=\"Small council\">small council</a> that there are upwards of two thousand <a href=\"/index.php/Sparrows\" title=\"Sparrows\">sparrows</a> within King's Landing and more arriving each day. He is among the two leading possibilities to replace the <a href=\"/index.php/High_Septon_(Tyrion%27s)\" title=\"High Septon (Tyrion&#39;s)\">deceased High Septon</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc17.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc17.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> Queen <a href=\"/index.php/Cersei_Lannister\" title=\"Cersei Lannister\">Cersei Lannister</a> visits Septon Raynard and Septon <a href=\"/index.php/Torbert\" title=\"Torbert\">Torbert</a> at the <a href=\"/index.php/Great_Sept_of_Baelor\" title=\"Great Sept of Baelor\">Great Sept of Baelor</a> and finds Raynard on his knees cleaning the floor. The <a href=\"/index.php/High_Sparrow\" title=\"High Sparrow\">High Sparrow</a>, the new High Septon, claims that doing work is pleasing to <a href=\"/index.php/Smith_(the_Seven)\" title=\"Smith (the Seven)\">the Smith</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc28.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc28.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>When the High Sparrow begins preaching against the brothels in <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a>, Cersei summons him to court to stop as brothels are a valued source of income for the crown. Instead the High Sparrow sends Raynard with an escort of six <a href=\"/index.php/Warrior%27s_Sons\" title=\"Warrior&#39;s Sons\">Warrior's Sons</a>. Raynard repeats the High Septon's words on the sinfulness of brothels which Cersei finds hypocritical, since she knows Raynard has \"special friends\" in half the brothels on the <a href=\"/index.php/Street_of_Silk\" title=\"Street of Silk\">Street of Silk</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Raynard&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Raffc17.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc17.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc17.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Chapter_17\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Chapter 17\">Chapter 17</a>, Cersei IV.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Raffc28.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc28.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">2.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc28.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\">2.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Chapter_28\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Chapter 28\">Chapter 28</a>, Cersei VI.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Raffc36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Chapter_36\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Chapter 36\">Chapter 36</a>, Cersei VIII.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403150850\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.067 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.246 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 622/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 10604/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 7710/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 448/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 2005/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.160/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.67 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  234.971      1 -total\n 84.05%  197.491      1 Template:Infobox_character\n 83.24%  195.583      1 Template:Infobox\n 11.64%   27.360      1 Template:Hatnote\n 10.78%   25.323     12 Template:Infobox_value\n  4.99%   11.731      4 Template:Infobox_label\n  3.22%    7.576      5 Template:Ref\n  1.72%    4.051      5 Template:Ref/core\n  0.90%    2.107      1 Template:References\n  0.39%    0.912      1 Template:Main_other\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:5429-0!canonical and timestamp 20260403150850 and revision id 315976\n -->\n",
